34#ifdef HAVE_CONFIG_H
35#include "config.h"
36#endif
37
38#include <sys/types.h>
39#include <sys/param.h>
40#include <sys/socket.h>
41
42#include PATH_IPSEC_H
43
44#include <net/pfkeyv2.h>
45
46#include "libpfkey.h"
47#include "ipsec_strerror.h"
48
49int
50ipsec_get_policylen(ipsec_policy_t policy)
51{
52 return policy ? PFKEY_EXTLEN(policy) : -1;
53}
